<script>
// RD Station Conversion Tracking
(function() {
  // Placeholder: Configure RD Station ID in variable
  var rdtn_id = '{{[92] RD Station Tracking ID}}';
  
  if (!rdtn_id || rdtn_id === 'PLACEHOLDER_RD_STATION_ID') {
    console.log('[92] RD Station: ID não configurado ainda');
    return;
  }
  
  // RD Station tracking code
  (function () {
    var s = document.createElement('script');
    s.type = 'text/javascript';
    s.async = true;
    s.src = 'https://d335luupugsy2.cloudfront.net/js/loader-scripts/'+rdtn_id+'-loader.js';
    var x = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
    x.parentNode.insertBefore(s, x);
  })();
  
  // Track conversion
  if (typeof RDStationTracking !== 'undefined') {
    RDStationTracking.track('conversion', {
      event_type: 'CONVERSION',
      event_family: 'CDP',
      payload: {
        conversion_identifier: '{{[92] DLV - conversion_identifier}}',
        email: '{{[92] DLV - email}}' || 'unknown@unknown.com',
        name: '{{[92] DLV - nome}}' || '',
        company: '{{[92] DLV - empresa}}' || '',
        personal_phone: '{{[92] DLV - telefone}}' || '',
        tags: ['lead', 'omma-engenharia'],
        traffic_source: '{{Traffic Source}}' || 'organic',
        traffic_medium: '{{Traffic Medium}}' || 'none',
        traffic_campaign: '{{Campaign}}' || '',
        available_for_mailing: true,
        legal_bases: [{
          category: 'consent',
          type: 'consent',
          status: 'granted'
        }]
      }
    });
  }
})();
</script>
